netactview (0.6.4-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Bugfix netactview release
    - Fixed processing of commands with invalid utf-8 characters and a related
      potential denial of service vulnerability.
    - Fixed configuration file validation to not allow huge configuration files
      and a related potential privilege authorization avoidance vulnerability.
    - Fixed the display of multiple multicast dns connections listening on the
      same port.
    - Fixed the connections list save when saving as root to a folder that the
      current sudo user can modify.
    - Limited the DNS cache to prevent it from becoming a memory leak.
    - Implemented a few other small fixes and defence in depth measures.

 -- Mihai Varzaru <mihaiv@gmail.com>  Sun, 29 Mar 2015 20:58:06 +0300


netactview (0.6.3-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Bugfix netactview release
    - Updated the location of the Wiki documentation to:
      http://netactview.sourceforge.net/wiki/
      The old wiki address will not be available after 2014-06-19 because
      sourceforge.net retires the hosted apps.
    - fixed the desktop file
    - fixed and updated the man file

 -- Mihai Varzaru <mihaiv@gmail.com>  Mon, 02 Jun 2014 11:16:01 +0300


